title: Spokane County Court House, Spokane, Washington
text: Postcard is of the Spokane County Courthouse in Spokane, Washington. Postmark 9/8/1912, Spokane, WA. Destination San Francisco, CA.
media_credit: Spokane Post Card Co., PG 107, Knowles Postcard Collection, University of Idaho Library Special Collections and Archives

title: Good News - Power
text: Psychiana radio program episode begins with assurance that there is a Power that can get people what they desire. Robinson then discusses his early life failures and childhood seeking of some force that could turn his failures into success. He asserts the God-Power can turn our failures into success and bring us material and spiritual abundance.
media_credit: Psychiana Digital Collection, Digital Initiatives, University of Idaho Library

title: University of Idaho vs. University of Southern California (Football)
text: Idaho Football vs. University of Southern California 10/30/1925 at Neale Stadium in Moscow, ID. Score: 7 - 51 (L).
